summary: This document is a certificate from the Department of Transportation certifying the authenticity of records related to a Gulfstream Aerospace aircraft. It includes signatures from officials confirming their roles and the validity of the records as of August 23, 2021.

persons.name: Michelle Endsley
persons.context: Michelle Endsley is identified as the legal custodian of the aircraft records and signed the certificate of true copy.

persons.name: Kevin R.
persons.context: Kevin R. is mentioned as the Acting Manager who also signed the document, affirming its authenticity.

keyFacts: The document certifies the authenticity of records related to Gulfstream Aerospace GI I 59B.
The aircraft was formerly registered as N909JE.
The certification was signed on August 23, 2021.
Michelle Endsley is the legal custodian of the records.
Kevin R. is the Acting Manager of the Aircraft Registration Branch.
